00:02:16.455 --> 00:02:17.955
So cosine of theta

00:02:20.263 --> 00:02:24.145
equals adjacent which is x, the x value,

00:02:24.145 --> 00:02:27.107
divided by hypotenuse which is one.

00:02:27.107 --> 00:02:29.825
So in this diagram, the cosine of theta

00:02:29.825 --> 00:02:34.238
